# Описываем Unet через Functional api

inp = keras.layers.Input(shape=(64, 64, 3))
x = inp

# encoder

x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=8, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=8, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
s1 = x
x = keras.layers.MaxPool2D(pool_size=(2, 2))(x)

x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=16, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=16, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
s2 = x
x = keras.layers.MaxPool2D(pool_size=(2, 2))(x)

x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=32, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=32, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
s3 = x
x = keras.layers.MaxPool2D(pool_size=(2, 2))(x)

x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=64, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=64, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)

# decoder
x = keras.layers.UpSampling2D(size=(2, 2))(x)
x = keras.layers.Concatenate(axis=-1)([x, s3])
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=32, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=32, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)

x = keras.layers.UpSampling2D(size=(2, 2))(x)
x = keras.layers.Concatenate(axis=-1)([x, s2])
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=16, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=16, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)

x = keras.layers.UpSampling2D(size=(2, 2))(x)
x = keras.layers.Concatenate(axis=-1)([x, s1])
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=8, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=8, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)

out = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=1, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
out = keras.layers.Activation('sigmoid', name='out')(out)

model = keras.models.Model(inputs=inp, outputs=out)


# Компилируем модель
sgd = keras.optimizers.SGD(lr=0.01, decay=1e-6, momentum=0.9, nesterov=True)
model.compile(optimizer=sgd, loss='binary_crossentropy')

# Описываем Unet c двумя головами через Functional api

inp = keras.layers.Input(shape=(64, 64, 3))
x = inp

# encoder

x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=8, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=8, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
s1 = x
x = keras.layers.MaxPool2D(pool_size=(2, 2))(x)

x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=16, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=16, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
s2 = x
x = keras.layers.MaxPool2D(pool_size=(2, 2))(x)

x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=32, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=32, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
s3 = x
x = keras.layers.MaxPool2D(pool_size=(2, 2))(x)

x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=64, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=64, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)

# decoder
x = keras.layers.UpSampling2D(size=(2, 2))(x)
x = keras.layers.Concatenate(axis=-1)([x, s3])
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=32, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=32, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)

x = keras.layers.UpSampling2D(size=(2, 2))(x)
x = keras.layers.Concatenate(axis=-1)([x, s2])
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=16, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=16, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)

x = keras.layers.UpSampling2D(size=(2, 2))(x)
x = keras.layers.Concatenate(axis=-1)([x, s1])
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=8, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=8, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)

out1 = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=1, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
out1 = keras.layers.Activation('sigmoid', name='out1')(out1)

out2 = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=1, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
out2 = keras.layers.Activation('linear', name='out2')(out2)

model = keras.models.Model(inputs=inp, outputs=[out1, out2])


# Компилируем модель
sgd = keras.optimizers.SGD(lr=0.01, decay=1e-6, momentum=0.9, nesterov=True)
model.compile(optimizer=sgd, loss=['binary_crossentropy', 'mean_squared_error'], loss_weights=[1.0, 0.5])

# Описываем Unet через Functional api c дополнительным входом

inp1 = keras.layers.Input(shape=(64, 64, 3))
x = inp1

inp2 = keras.layers.Input(shape=(1, 1, 10))
b = inp2

# branch

b = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=16, kernel_size=(1, 1), padding='valid')(b)
b = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(b)
b = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=16, kernel_size=(1, 1), padding='valid')(b)
b = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(b)

b = keras.layers.UpSampling2D(size=(8, 8))(b)

# encoder

x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=8, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=8, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
s1 = x
x = keras.layers.MaxPool2D(pool_size=(2, 2))(x)

x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=16, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=16, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
s2 = x
x = keras.layers.MaxPool2D(pool_size=(2, 2))(x)

x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=32, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=32, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
s3 = x
x = keras.layers.MaxPool2D(pool_size=(2, 2))(x)

x = keras.layers.Concatenate(axis=-1)([x, b])
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=64, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=64, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)

# decoder
x = keras.layers.UpSampling2D(size=(2, 2))(x)
x = keras.layers.Concatenate(axis=-1)([x, s3])
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=32, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=32, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)

x = keras.layers.UpSampling2D(size=(2, 2))(x)
x = keras.layers.Concatenate(axis=-1)([x, s2])
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=16, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=16, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)

x = keras.layers.UpSampling2D(size=(2, 2))(x)
x = keras.layers.Concatenate(axis=-1)([x, s1])
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=8, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=8, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)

out = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=1, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
out = keras.layers.Activation('sigmoid', name='out')(out)

model = keras.models.Model(inputs=[inp1, inp2], outputs=out)


# Компилируем модель
sgd = keras.optimizers.SGD(lr=0.01, decay=1e-6, momentum=0.9, nesterov=True)
model.compile(optimizer=sgd, loss='binary_crossentropy')

# Описываем Unet через Functional api с использованием блоков

def MyBlock(filters, repeats):
    def f(x):
        for i in range(repeats):
            x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=filters, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
            x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
        return x
    return f


inp = keras.layers.Input(shape=(64, 64, 3))
x = inp

# encoder

x = MyBlock(filters=8, repeats=2)(x)
s1 = x
x = keras.layers.MaxPool2D(pool_size=(2, 2))(x)

x = MyBlock(filters=16, repeats=2)(x)
s2 = x
x = keras.layers.MaxPool2D(pool_size=(2, 2))(x)

x = MyBlock(filters=32, repeats=2)(x)
s3 = x
x = keras.layers.MaxPool2D(pool_size=(2, 2))(x)

x = MyBlock(filters=64, repeats=2)(x)

# decoder
x = keras.layers.UpSampling2D(size=(2, 2))(x)
x = keras.layers.Concatenate(axis=-1)([x, s3])
x = MyBlock(filters=32, repeats=2)(x)

x = keras.layers.UpSampling2D(size=(2, 2))(x)
x = keras.layers.Concatenate(axis=-1)([x, s2])
x = MyBlock(filters=16, repeats=2)(x)

x = keras.layers.UpSampling2D(size=(2, 2))(x)
x = keras.layers.Concatenate(axis=-1)([x, s1])
x = MyBlock(filters=8, repeats=2)(x)

out = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=1, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
out = keras.layers.Activation('sigmoid', name='out')(out)

model = keras.models.Model(inputs=inp, outputs=out)


# Компилируем модель
sgd = keras.optimizers.SGD(lr=0.01, decay=1e-6, momentum=0.9, nesterov=True)
model.compile(optimizer=sgd, loss='binary_crossentropy')

# Полностью параметризуем Unet

def MyBlock(filters, repeats):
    def f(x):
        for i in range(repeats):
            x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=filters, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
            x = keras.layers.Activation('relu')(x)
        return x
    return f


def MyUnet(filters_init, filters_mul, repeats, steps):
    def f(x):
        i_s_list = []
        # encoder
        for i in range(steps):
            x = MyBlock(filters=int(filters_init*filters_mul**i), repeats=repeats)(x)
            i_s_list.append((i, x))
            x = keras.layers.MaxPool2D(pool_size=(2, 2))(x)
        x = MyBlock(filters=int(filters_init*filters_mul**(i+1)), repeats=repeats)(x)
        # decoder
        for i, s in i_s_list[::-1]:
            x = keras.layers.UpSampling2D(size=(2, 2))(x)
            x = keras.layers.Concatenate(axis=-1)([x, s])
            x = MyBlock(filters=int(filters_init*filters_mul**i), repeats=repeats)(x)
        x = keras.layers.Conv2D(filters=1, kernel_size=(3, 3), padding='same')(x)
        x = keras.layers.Activation('sigmoid', name='out')(x)
        return x
    return f


inp = keras.layers.Input(shape=(64, 64, 3))
out = MyUnet(filters_init=8, filters_mul=2, repeats=2, steps=3)(inp)

model = keras.models.Model(inputs=inp, outputs=out)


# Компилируем модель
sgd = keras.optimizers.SGD(lr=0.01, decay=1e-6, momentum=0.9, nesterov=True)
model.compile(optimizer=sgd, loss='binary_crossentropy')
